\"Mixed Seeds\">Mixed Seeds</a> • <a href=\"/Mossy_Seed\" title=\"Mossy Seed\">Mossy Seed</a> • <a href=\"/Mushroom_Tree_Seed\" title=\"Mushroom Tree Seed\">Mushroom Tree Seed</a> • <a href=\"/Mystic_Tree_Seed\" title=\"Mystic Tree Seed\">Mystic Tree Seed</a> • <a href=\"/Pineapple_Seeds\" title=\"Pineapple Seeds\">Pineapple Seeds</a> • <a href=\"/Qi_Bean\" title=\"Qi Bean\">Qi Bean</a> • <a href=\"/Tea_Sapling\" title=\"Tea Sapling\">Tea Sapling</a> • <a href=\"/Pine_Cone\" title=\"Pine Cone\">Pine Cone</a> • <a href=\"/Taro_Tuber\" title=\"Taro Tuber\">Taro Tuber</a>\n</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260413165635\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nComplications: []\nCPU time usage: 0.111 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.132 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1090/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 16076/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1801/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 376/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.004/7.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 653 KB/50 MB\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   57.368      1 -total\n 69.44%   39.839      1 Template:Infobox_seed\n 22.51%   12.913      2 Template:Tprice\n 20.42%   11.716      1 Template:Description\n 15.42%    8.847      1 Template:Name\n  8.02%    4.602      1 Template:GiftsByItem\n  6.21%    3.564      7 Template:Price\n  2.39%    1.373      1 Template:NavboxSeeds\n  2.34%    1.345      1 Template:InfoboxSEO\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key enwiki:pcache:idhash:3186-0!canonical and timestamp 20260413165635 and revision id 191953\n -->\n</div>",
      "wikitext": "{{Infobox seed\n|image     = Rare Seed.png\n|crop      = {{Name|Sweet Gem Berry}}\n|growth    = 24 days\n|season    = Fall\n|sellprice = {{Price|200}}\n|gPrice    = Not Sold\n|jPrice    = Not Sold\n|tPrice    = {{Price|1000}} (Spring and Summer)<br />{{tprice|200}} (1.26% chance, any season)\n}}\nThe '''Rare Seed''' is a type of seed. A mature plant yields a [[Sweet Gem Berry]].\n\nOne to five Rare Seeds can be purchased at the [[Traveling Cart]] for {{Price|1000}} each during [[Spring]] and [[Summer]].  During any season, there is also a 1.26% chance that the merchant will be selling 1-5 Rare Seeds for {{tprice|200}} each. (It is possible for Rare Seeds to occupy two slots in the merchant's offerings in Spring and Summer).  Rare Seeds can also be obtained by using the [[Seed Maker]]. \n\nDespite the description stating that this seed \"''takes all season to grow''\", it takes only 24 days.  If using [[fertilizer]] that speeds crop growth or having the [[Farming#Farming Skill|Agriculturist Profession]], it will take fewer days.\n\n==Stages==\n{{#lsth:Sweet Gem Berry|Stages}}\n\n==Gifting==\n{{GiftsByItem\n|dislike=Robin,Demetrius,Maru,Sebastian,Linus,Pierre,Caroline,Abigail,Alex,George,Evelyn,Lewis,Clint,Penny,Pam,Emily,Haley,Jas,Vincent,Jodi,Kent,Sam,Leah,Shane,Marnie,Elliott,Gus,Dwarf,Wizard,Harvey,Sandy,Willy,Krobus,Leo\n}}\n\n==Tips==\n*The Seed Maker creates an average of two seeds from one [[Sweet Gem Berry]] 97.5% of the time. Since a [[Sweet Gem Berry]] is worth at least {{Price|3000}}, each Rare Seed produced from the Seed Maker is created at a cost of {{Price|1500}} to {{Price|3000}} depending on the quality of the input. This makes the maximum price of {{Price|1000}} at the [[Traveling Cart]] a much better buy, even though the quantities offered there are limited.\n\n==Notes==\nA [[Livin' Off The Land]] tip (Fall 1, Year 2) informs the player that Rare Seeds take only 24 days to grow, and not a full season (28 days). \n\n{{NavboxSeeds}}